00:00:47.583 --> 00:00:48.042
Sorry?

00:00:48.167 --> 00:00:49.333
Senior peon,

00:00:49.458 --> 00:00:50.417
senior clerk,

00:00:50.542 --> 00:00:51.875
senior typist senior what?

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:52.792
Bloody hell, he wasn't a dad-

00:00:52.917 --> 00:00:53.917
